sequenceDiagram
  actor User
  participant CLI as CLI or UI
  participant API as Local API
  participant Store as SQLite KB Store
  participant AI as AI Package
  participant OpenAI as OpenAI API

  User->>CLI: ask question
  opt UI request
    CLI->>API: POST /api/kbs/:kb/ask
  end
  API->>Store: searchEvidence(question)
  Store-->>API: graph nodes, edges, files, repos
  API->>AI: answerQuestion(evidence)
  alt OPENAI_API_KEY set
    AI->>OpenAI: send compact graph evidence
    OpenAI-->>AI: grounded answer
    AI-->>API: OpenAI answer
  else no key or API failure
    AI-->>API: deterministic graph-backed answer
  end
  API-->>CLI: answer + evidence metadata
  CLI-->>User: answer
